cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper deals with range-based positioning techniques using Wi-Fi devices in an indoor environment. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes an unsupervised learning technique to obtain the coordinates of unknown nodes. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the proposed method involves machine learning and automated discovery of unknown nodes. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with estimating coordinates in a physical space. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with improving the accuracy of positioning systems.
